SELECT * FROM IT01_FlotteOraniHesaplamaTipleri FOHT

SELECT * FROM IT01_CozeltiHesapTipleri CHT

SELECT UPT.FlotteOranHesapTipID, UPT.VarsCozeltiHesapTipID, P.ProsesAdi FROM IT01_Prosesler P
INNER JOIN IT01_UretimPartiTipleri UPT On UPT.UretimPartiTipID = P.UretimPartiTipID
Where P.IsReceteli  =1
